    "description": "Slide and jump over the procedurally generated maps. Avoid the red blocks, or hitting the edge of a white block. Fast and furious. Are your reactions quick enough?<br><br>The map moves quickly to the left. You need to slide along the wide platforms, and jump over the red blocks, and over the barriers, to get to the end of the map. You can control the difficulty of the map by changing the speed, the number of red blocks, and the number of distractor white blocks. There are an effectively infinite number of procedurally generated maps available.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183040/extras/5585913953b9aadfdfe36f368dd26d92.avif?t=1666045482\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183040/extras_big/5585913953b9aadfdfe36f368dd26d92.avif?t=1666045482 width=800 height=598 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183040/extras/1fb538109f9ffe0eaa847f6fc57c42d6.poster.avif?t=1666045482\" width=500 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183040/extras/1fb538109f9ffe0eaa847f6fc57c42d6.webm?t=1666045482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183040/extras/1fb538109f9ffe0eaa847f6fc57c42d6.mp4?t=1666045482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
